Hi Ian,
Not sure it's still useful after patch provide by Prasanna...
But I tried to turn off CONFIG_DEBUG_RODATA and both `tcp_probe' and
`dccp_probe' can be load properly.
I also ran iperf test (for dccp) and it works.
Patrick.
